ate": "2026-06-30T19:42:50Z", "likes": 79, "url": "https://x.com/Clevta/status/2072043202014535730", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072043011496956266", "handle": "RecepPerception", "name": null, "text": "Check out the full season analysis from @MattHarmon_BYB and what contributed to the special season", "date": "2026-06-30T19:42:05Z", "likes": 8, "url": "https://x.com/RecepPerception/status/2072043011496956266", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "Matt Harmon reposted", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072043004677046392", "handle": "RecepPerception", "name": null, "text": "Best way to describe JSN's breakout season? ELITE", "date": "2026-06-30T19:42:03Z", "likes": 11, "url": "https://x.com/RecepPerception/status/2072043004677046392", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "Matt Harmon reposted", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072041998723252247", "handle": "Clevta", "name": null, "text": "I'd look to teams like CHI, Brooklyn and Utah in a potential salary shedding trade. CHI could just take Strus for a 2nd rd pick and absorb his contract for ex.", "date": "2026-06-30T19:38:03Z", "likes": 12, "url": "https://x.com/Clevta/status/2072041998723252247", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072041607805763736", "handle": "DhananiZain", "name": null, "text": "Shane Waldron got promoted - added \"Assistant Head Coach\" to his title", "date": "2026-06-30T19:36:30Z", "likes": 17, "url": "https://x.com/DhananiZain/status/2072041607805763736", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072041297993719975", "handle": "HaydenWinks", "name": null, "text": "my ankle would look like skattebo's if i tried this", "date": "2026-06-30T19:35:16Z", "likes": 102, "url": "https://x.com/HaydenWinks/status/2072041297993719975", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072039196945231997", "handle": "HaydenWinks", "name": null, "text": "The 2025 results at QB completely backed up what the data was showing for the previous 5 years of best ball. The math mathed.", "date": "2026-06-30T19:26:55Z", "likes": 44, "url": "https://x.com/HaydenWinks/status/2072039196945231997", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072038413537362281", "handle": "JakeLFischer", "name": null, "text": "Amid LeBron James' impending exit from Los Angeles, sources say the Cavaliers have held ongoing trade conversations regarding veterans Max Strus and Dennis Schröder, which could help Cleveland free the space to add James, and also benefit the Cavs' effort to retain Dean Wade.", "date": "2026-06-30T19:23:49Z", "likes": 468, "url": "https://x.com/JakeLFischer/status/2072038413537362281", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "Clevta reposted", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072037959491072105", "handle": "Clevta", "name": null, "text": "Big move just came on the cavs out of nowhere on kalshi. Must be the Vardon tweet. The Cavs are now the leaders in the clubhouse", "date": "2026-06-30T19:22:00Z", "likes": 120, "url": "https://x.com/Clevta/status/2072037959491072105", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072037542568862033", "handle": "smitchell17", "name": null, "text": "I'd much rather sweat a little bit than not be able to feel my nose, toes, or fingers No thanks", "date": "2026-06-30T19:20:21Z", "likes": 9, "url": "https://x.com/smitchell17/status/2072037542568862033", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072037362285019510", "handle": "Clevta", "name": null, "text": "Sequence of events if LBJ to the Cavs is actually real. They'd have to dump Strus or Schroeder first to offer the mid level. If that happens then its sirens up from there... Or he signs with GS today and its all moot", "date": "2026-06-30T19:19:38Z", "likes": 41, "url": "https://x.com/Clevta/status/2072037362285019510", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072036754245255638", "handle": "4for4football", "name": null, "text": "Players On Bad Teams Can Be Good For Fantasy Football", "date": "2026-06-30T19:17:13Z", "likes": 0, "url": "https://x.com/4for4football/status/2072036754245255638", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072035484268716480", "handle": "JakobSanderson", "name": null, "text": "Rome Odunze has a career YPRR of 1.33 Marvin Harrison has a career YPRR of 1.61 If one of these WRs is going to make a Y3 leap I'm betting on the far better prospect -- who has also been better in the NFL despite being talked about as a far larger disappointment", "date": "2026-06-30T19:12:10Z", "likes": 92, "url": "https://x.com/JakobSanderson/status/2072035484268716480", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072034685996126241", "handle": "ohnohedidnt24", "name": null, "text": "Kendrick Perkins: \"Rich Paul, little turtle head snotty nose ass called me all throughout the season every time I'm on TV I get a text message from him. I've been calling him for 2 days now and he been ignoring me. We got a problem\"", "date": "2026-06-30T19:09:00Z", "likes": 4993, "url": "https://x.com/ohnohedidnt24/status/2072034685996126241", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "Clevta reposted", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072034436040753431", "handle": "fball_insights", "name": null, "text": "Defensive play caller efficiency splits vs play action dating back to 2012 Mike Macdonald up there with Belichick", "date": "2026-06-30T19:08:00Z", "likes": 55, "url": "https://x.com/fball_insights/status/2072034436040753431", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072034255216038148", "handle": "ScottBarrettDFB", "name": null, "text": "Killer debut piece by @DhananiZain looking into the importance of route depth for WRs Contrary to public opinion, WRs who run deeper route trees are NOT \"higher-ceiling\" on a weekly basis", "date": "2026-06-30T19:07:17Z", "likes": 26, "url": "https://x.com/ScottBarrettDFB/status/2072034255216038148", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072032745115517329", "handle": "MikeClayNFL", "name": null, "text": "Will JSN help you roll to another fantasy title in 2026?", "date": "2026-06-30T19:01:17Z", "likes": 27, "url": "https://x.com/MikeClayNFL/status/2072032745115517329", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2072032157749641680", "handle": "CTM_Show", "name": null, "text": "Steve and Sam debate where Matthew Stafford falls in the top QB conversation “If you really look at Stafford's five-year career with the Rams, the Super Bowl run was excellent. 2022 was a disappointment, 2023 was excellent and underrated, and 2024 was a disappointment for”", "date": "2026-06-30T18:58:57Z", "likes": 3, "url": "https://x.com/CTM_Show/status/2072032157749641680", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "Sam Monson reposted", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2071984585311707397", "handle": "KevHarlanEffect", "name": null, "text": "“I was just talking to Kevin O'Connell.”", "date": "2026-06-30T15:49:55Z", "likes": 8010, "url": "https://x.com/KevHarlanEffect/status/2071984585311707397", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "Sean Koerner reposted", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}, {"id": "2071972456194040235", "handle": "UDFootballShow", "name": null, "text": "If that was actually Xavier Worthy running around in the grass, @HaydenWinks owes everyone an apology", "date": "2026-06-30T15:01:43Z", "likes": 35, "url": "https://x.com/UDFootballShow/status/2071972456194040235", "kind": "tweet", "has_media": false, "social": "Josh Norris reposted", "source": "x_list_scroll", "first_seen": "2026-07-01T00:37:30+00:00"}]}